NOTICE OF CLAIM OF LIEN FOR DELINQUENT ASSESSMENTS
NOTICE IS HEREBY GIVEN: Red Rock Financial Services, a division of FirstService Residential,
Nevada, LLC, has been assigned as agent by the Cottage Grove Estates Homeowners Association, Inc (the
"Association"), in accordance with Nevada Revised Statues Chapter 116 and the Association's Covenants,
Conditions, and Restrictions, as amended and/or annexed (the "CC&Rs"), recorded on 07/18/2006, in Book
Number , as Instrument Number 663149, of the Official Records of Nye County, Nevada, which CC&Rs have
been supplied to and agreed upon by said owner.
The Association imposes a Lien for Delinquent Assessments on the following property:
50 S Weeping Willow Ct Pahrump NV 89048
COTTAGE GROVE ESTATES LOT 3 BLOCK 2 in the County of Nye
Current Owner(s) of Record for the property:/
LINDA C BACON-KENDALL
The amount owing as of the date of preparation of this lien is ** $1,219.20.
This amount may include assessments, late fees, interest, fines/violations, including fine(s) for violation(s) of
the governing documents that pose an imminent threat of causing a substantial adverse effect on the health,
safety or welfare of the owners of 50 S Weeping Willow Ct or the Association's residents, and collection fees
and costs.
** The amount owing may increase or decrease as assessments, late fees, interest, fines/violations, collection fees,
costs or partial payments are applied to the account.
Dated: May 13, 2021
Prepared By DezeJuania Moore, Red Rock Financial Services, on behalf of Cottage Grove Estates
Homeowners Association, Inc
STATE OF NEVADA
COUNTY OF CLARK
On May 13, 2021, before me, personally appeared DezeJuania Moore, personally known to me (or proved to
me on the basis of satisfactory evidence) to be the person whose name is subscribed to the within instrument
and acknowledged to me that they executed the same in their authorized capacity, and that by their signature on
the instrument the person, or the entity upon behalf of which the person acted, executed the instrument.
WITNESS my hand and official seal.
Biendes Haunandless
Brianda Hamandez
Notary Public
